The Leftovers S01E00 - Making The Leftovers

This episode goes behind the scenes of the upcoming HBO series "The Leftovers". The series follows a group of people in the suburban community of Mapleton who are left behind after the sudden disappearance of millions of people worldwide.

A variety of people involved in the show provide insight, including the author, Tom Perrotta, co-creator Damon Lindelof, director Peter Berg and cast members such as Liv Tyler, Christopher Eccleston, Justin Theroux and Scott Glenn.

This aired on HBO HD on June 22, 2014. The series starts on June 29, 2014.
